* Communicating with goroutines (cont.)

- Stage 3: Stitching up the GIF
- use the tomb package that encapsulates the goroutine signalling pattern

    type GifWriter struct {
        Tombstone tomb.Tomb
    }

- Cooperatively stop a running goroutine 

    var task3    *io.GifWriter
    task3.Run(vr, args)

    time.Sleep(1 * time.Second)
    log.Fatal(task3.Stop()) // calls tomb.Kill(nil)

- Or wait for the result/error

    if err := task3.Tombstone.Wait(); err != nil {
        syscall.Exit(126)
    }

